      <title>游日时罗马仕尿袋爆炸，炸㶶地板，被日本住宿收¥15 万维修费</title>
      <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/06/21/romoss-powerbank-fire-recall/mobile-phone/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=romoss-powerbank-fire-recall</link>
