    <item>
      <title>Polestar 3 与 Volvo XC90 登升香港， 北欧美学与安全理念全面进化</title>
      <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/06/21/polestar3-vovlo-xc90-hk-launch/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=polestar3-vovlo-xc90-hk-launch</link>
      <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/06/21/polestar3-vovlo-xc90-hk-launch/life-tech/auto/#respond</comments>
      <dc:creator>arthur</dc:creator>
      <pubDate>Sat, 21 Jun 2025 05:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <category>汽车科技</category>
      <category>科技新闻</category>
      <category>polestar</category>
      <category>Volvo</category>
      <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1313112</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;香港高端 SUV 市场再添两款新选择，属同一集团的 Polestar 和 Volvo 同日发表两款旗舰级豪华 SUV：纯电动的 Polestar 3 与最新一代油电混能 XC90 SUV。两车除拥有简约北欧设计待格外，更分别聚焦电动性能与安全科技，满足不同用户对豪华、实用的追求。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1313114" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/img_20250620_162042-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/img_20250620_162042-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/img_20250620_162042-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Polestar 3 首度抵港，定位品牌电动阵容中最高阶型号，结合强悍动力与简约设计。高阶双摩打性能版提供高达 517 匹马力与 910Nm 扭力，加速至 100 公里仅需 4.7 秒，搭配主动空气悬挂及扭矩矢量控制系统，在弯路与高速巡航中均展现出色表现。另一款单摩打版本则主打续航力，具备后驱配置与 706 公里 WLTP 续航距离，适合香港市区与郊区之间频繁通勤的驾驶需求。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1313113" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/img_20250620_162012-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/img_20250620_162012-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/img_20250620_162012-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1313115" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/img_20250620_162407-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/img_20250620_162407-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/img_20250620_162407-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Polestar 3 的外形强调空气动力学与北欧极简美学，采用低矮车顶线与流线轮廓，配备 Smart Zone 感应科技模组，融合前视镜头与感应器，取代传统鬼面罩设计。车舱内部配备全景玻璃车顶与高质感饰材，并搭载 Bowers &amp;amp; Wilkins 25 扬声器系统与 14.5 吋 Android 中控屏幕，支援 Apple CarPlay 和 Google 应用整合，为车主带来沉浸式的多媒体体验。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1313116" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/img_20250620_162434-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/img_20250620_162434-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/img_20250620_162434-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1313119" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/img_20250620_162625-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/img_20250620_162625-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/img_20250620_162625-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;与此同时，Volvo XC90 亦以全新姿态回归香港市场。作为 Volvo 品牌 SUV 旗舰，XC90 承袭过往在安全领域的传奇表现，凭借连续 6 年获得 IIHS「Top Safety Pick+」与 Euro NCAP 五星评级，进一步巩固其「安全标杆」地位。新款 XC90 搭载轻混能引擎系统与全轮驱动技术，在高效与舒适之间取得平衡，配合全新隔音升级，在行驶期间提供更静谧的座舱环境。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1313120" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/img_20250620_170426-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/img_20250620_170426-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/img_20250620_170426-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1313121" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/img_20250620_164325-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/img_20250620_164325-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/img_20250620_164325-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1313122" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/img_20250620_165411-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/img_20250620_165411-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/img_20250620_165411-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;新 XC90 提供 B5 Plus 和 B5 Ultra 两个版本，前者标配 Nordico 环保材质座椅与 Harman Kardon 音响，后者则进一步升级至 Nappa 真皮座椅与 Bowers &amp;amp; Wilkins 顶级音响，带来更细致的声效与豪华感。七座设计，兼顾家庭与商务出行，后排座椅设有专属冷气与遮阳设备，进一步提升乘坐舒适度。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1313123" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/img_20250620_165508-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/img_20250620_165508-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/img_20250620_165508-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1313124" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/img_20250620_165515-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/img_20250620_165515-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/img_20250620_165515-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Volvo 在空气品质方面亦有所突破，全新 XC90 引入四区恒温空调与 PM2.5 空气监测系统，搭载高效净化器可过滤 95% 以上 PM0.3 微粒，获国际机构认证为哮喘与过敏友好设计。外观方面，重新设计的 LED 头灯与大型鬼面罩令车身更具力量感，多款新色如 Mulberry Red 与 Vapour Grey，则为消费者提供更多个性化选项。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;价格方面，Polestar 3 单摩打版本售价为 HK$755,500，合资格参加政府「一换一」计划；长续航双摩打版及高性能双摩打版售价分别为 HK$1,349,900 及 HK$1,449,900；Volvo XC90 则分别定价 HK$799,900（B5 Plus）与 HK$899,900（B5 Ultra）。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;&lt;b&gt;
